text: Gei taane gu hagalee hiihai e noho i di boo labelaa i golo, gei mee mo dono lodo hege ga daamada gaa hula, mo dana dangada hai hegau mo ana manu ‘donkey’ e lua mo nia hii goloo nonua. Di nadau hoohoo gi Jebus, dela go Jerusalem, ge di maa gu hoohoo gi di hiahi, tangada hai hegau ga helekai gi dono dagi, “Gidaadou e aha ala hagalee noho i ginei i lodo di waahale digau Jebus?”
